# Tailwind CSS

> Utility-first CSS framework for rapidly building custom designs without leaving your HTML.

---

## Overview

Tailwind CSS is a utility-first CSS framework that provides:
- **Utility Classes**: Pre-built classes for every CSS property
- **Design System**: Built-in spacing, colors, typography scales
- **Responsive**: Mobile-first breakpoint system
- **Dark Mode**: Built-in dark mode support
- **JIT Engine**: On-demand CSS generation

---

## Why Tailwind

| Benefit | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| Speed | Style without context-switching to CSS files |
| Consistency | Built-in design system with constraints |
| Size | Only includes CSS you actually use |
| Maintainability | No dead CSS, co-located styles |
| Customization | Fully configurable design tokens |

