## Layout

### Flexbox

```html
<!-- Basic flex container -->
<div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
  <div>Left</div>
  <div>Right</div>
</div>

<!-- Flex direction -->
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
  <div class="flex-1">Grows</div>
  <div class="flex-none">Fixed</div>
  <div class="flex-shrink-0">No shrink</div>
</div>

<!-- Common patterns -->
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">           <!-- Wrap items -->
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">        <!-- Vertical center -->
<div class="flex justify-center">            <!-- Horizontal center -->
<div class="flex items-center justify-center"> <!-- Full center -->
```

### Grid

```html
<!-- Basic grid -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
  <div>1</div>
  <div>2</div>
  <div>3</div>
</div>

<!-- Responsive grid -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
  <!-- Items -->
</div>

<!-- Column spanning -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4">
  <div class="col-span-2">Half width</div>
  <div class="col-span-1">Quarter</div>
  <div class="col-span-1">Quarter</div>
</div>

<!-- Auto-fit responsive grid -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-[repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr))] gap-4">
  <!-- Auto-adjusting items -->
</div>
```

### Spacing

```html
<!-- Margin -->
<div class="m-4">      <!-- All sides: 1rem -->
<div class="mx-auto">  <!-- Horizontal center -->
<div class="mt-8">     <!-- Top only: 2rem -->
<div class="mb-4">     <!-- Bottom only -->
<div class="ml-2">     <!-- Left only -->
<div class="mr-2">     <!-- Right only -->

<!-- Padding -->
<div class="p-6">      <!-- All sides -->
<div class="px-4 py-2"> <!-- Horizontal & vertical -->
<div class="pt-8">     <!-- Top only -->

<!-- Space between children -->
<div class="space-y-4"> <!-- Vertical spacing -->
<div class="space-x-2"> <!-- Horizontal spacing -->

<!-- Gap (flex/grid) -->
<div class="flex gap-4">
<div class="grid gap-6">
```

| Scale | Value |
|-------|-------|
| `0` | 0px |
| `1` | 0.25rem (4px) |
| `2` | 0.5rem (8px) |
| `4` | 1rem (16px) |
| `6` | 1.5rem (24px) |
| `8` | 2rem (32px) |
| `12` | 3rem (48px) |
| `16` | 4rem (64px) |

