## Best Practices

### Do

```html
<!-- Use semantic component patterns -->
<article class="prose"> <!-- Typography plugin -->
  <h1>Title</h1>
  <p>Content...</p>
</article>

<!-- Extract repeated patterns to components -->
<!-- Button.tsx -->
<button className={cn(
  "px-4 py-2 rounded-md transition-colors",
  variant === "primary" && "bg-blue-500 text-white",
  variant === "secondary" && "bg-gray-100 text-gray-700"
)}>

<!-- Use @apply sparingly for base styles -->
/* globals.css */
@layer base {
  body {
    @apply bg-white text-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100;
  }
}
```

### Don't

```html
<!-- Don't repeat long class strings - extract to components -->
<!-- Bad -->
<button class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-600">
<button class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-600">
<button class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-600">

<!-- Don't fight the framework with excessive arbitrary values -->
<!-- If you need many custom values, extend the config instead -->
```

